This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/CMSPlaceOfServiceCS defines the following codes:

CodeDefinition

name: CMSPlaceOfServiceCS
title: CMS Place of Service
description:
https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/place-of-service-codes/Place_of_Service_Code_Set.html .   
The link takes one to the Place of Service list as an html document; it is not a file to which an IG can be bound.  
The code set is owned by CMS and is available for use.
